    "title": "The Pale Blue Fire",
    "biomes": ["forest"],
    "weight": 8,
    "one_shot": false,
    "text": "A small blue flame floats at eye level between the trees, about thirty feet off the path. It doesn't flicker. It moves—drifting left, then stopping, then drifting again—like something looking for the right direction.",
