    "biomes": ["forest"],
    "weight": 8,
    "one_shot": false,
    "text": "A massive oak is covered in carved names—hundreds of them, layered over decades or longer. Some are still sharp. Some are nearly grown over. One of them, near eye level, is your leader's name. Or something very close to it.",
